b'Mayonaka wa Junketsu':
b'The story is that a mysterious woman fights with a baldheaded leader of an evil secret society. Sheena played the woman and Masato Minagawa, a keyboard player of her band, played the enemy's leader.

Her pet cat "Goethe" also appears in the music video as a cyborg cat. The heroine was named "Mayo Kiyozumi" (\xe6\xbd\x94\xe7\xb4\x94\xe7\x9c\x9f\xe5\xa4\x9c Kiyozumi Mayo) according to the anagram of the song title.

(Source: Wikipedia)'
